OL,3,CMan pleads guilty to theft of #80,000
OL,4,Ccandelabra from Welsh castle
OL,6,FA man has pleaded guilty to stealing a
OL,7,Fcandelabra worth #80,000 from
OL,8,FCyfarthfa Castle in Merthyr Tydfil in
OL,9,FApril.
OL,11,FHenry Tyson Wilsher, 31, walked out of
OL,12,Fthe museum with the valuable object
OL,13,Fback in April after smashing a glass
OL,14,Fcabinet to steal it, shocking staff
OL,15,Fand schoolchildren who were on a
OL,16,Fschool trip at the time.
