OL,3,CMan pleads guilty to theft of #80,000
OL,4,Ccandelabra from Welsh castle
OL,6,FSouth Wales Police launched a manhunt
OL,7,Fto try and find the thief, and the
OL,8,FLeicestershire man has appeared in
OL,9,Fcourt in connection with the incident
OL,10,Fon 8 April.
OL,12,FAppearing via video link before
OL,13,FTeeside Magistrates' Court on Tuesday,
OL,14,F24 June, Wilsher pleaded guilty to
OL,15,Ftheft, receiving stolen goods, and
OL,16,Fcriminal damage.
