OL,3,CMan pleads guilty to theft of #80,000
OL,4,Ccandelabra from Welsh castle
OL,6,FHe admitted stealing the candelabra
OL,7,Ffrom the castle, dishonestly receiving
OL,8,Fa Ford Fiesta knowing or believing it
OL,9,Fto be stolen, and criminal damage
OL,10,Fafter damaging a glass cabinet to
OL,11,Faccess the candelabra.
OL,13,FThe court heard that the candelabra -
OL,14,Fone of the museum's most prized
OL,15,Fobjects - is yet to be recovered.
OL,17,FWilsher, of Bagworth in
OL,18,FLeicestershire, was remanded in
OL,19,Fcustody and is due to be sentenced at
OL,20,FTeesside Crown Court on 15 July.
