OL,4,Ccandelabra from Welsh castle
OL,6,FMerthyr Tydfil Council leader Brent
OL,7,FCarter previously told ITV Wales of
OL,8,Fthe "frightening" incident: "It was
OL,9,Fawful. There were sixty schoolchildren
OL,10,Fhere from Cyfarthfa Park Primary.
OL,12,F"They were here enjoying themselves,
OL,13,Flooking around the museum, and a
OL,14,Fgentleman came in, picked a house
OL,15,Fbrick out of his pocket, and smashed
OL,16,Fthe casing, tore back the glass and
OL,17,Fstole the candelabra."
